{
  "stem": "4226.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, next, next day, they took us in time out to a place called-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the name of the place-- outside Munich.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had enough time to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Can't remember the name now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went, went until we come to the river-- Isar was the river-- on the banks of Isar.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the German guard thought it's safe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the bombers started coming towards Munich, we saw them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were in a field.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And not far from us in the fields were corn fields, big flag batteries' cannons started coming up, the whole group, eight of them, and started opening fire on the things.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The guards started back on the truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Clear out of here because they will cop it because of their anti--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--aircraft batteries.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we, we had about two weeks working on this Bahnhof until we got back to our normal work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the railway yards, we, we had to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, mind you, first time we saw-- we, we got some biscuits and, and some lollies dropped at us from some civilian German women.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And over, over the-- they had this little walkway over the tracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were working, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew we were prisoners, but I don't think they knew we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] In, in Dachau, in [NON-ENGLISH], when I was working those 10 days, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] German kids, boys and girls, I could see them talking.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They thought we, we were [GERMAN], criminals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They went over to the other side of the road because we were sitting on the footpaths there having lunch, or eating our bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We couldn't stop them in telling them who we are, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
